### ============================================================================
### ⚙️ CONFIGURAÇÕES GLOBAIS
### ============================================================================
@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080

# IDs reais capturados dos seus logs de sucesso
@subscriberUid = d0cf8fa5-840e-46eb-991d-d8137998f4f7
@adminUid = eafcbb0c-e7e4-41e3-88c0-1344176cee61
@walletUid = <preencha_aqui_apos_o_post_de_abrir_carteira>

# Credenciais provisionadas pelo SeedDatabaseConfig
@rootEmail = master@invest.com
@rootPass = invest_2026_secure

# Credenciais do usuário criado no seu teste
@clientEmail = investidor@exemplo.com
@clientPass = senha_segura_123

### ============================================================================
### 👤 GERENCIAMENTO DE CONTAS (SUBSCRIBERS)
### ============================================================================

### 1. Criar Novo Assinante (Standard User)
# Rota pública conforme SecurityServiceGateway
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/accounts/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "fullName": "João Investidor",
  "contactEmail": "investidor@exemplo.com",
  "secretKey": "senha_segura_123",
  "accessLevel": "STANDARD_USER"
}

### 2. Listar Todos os Perfis (Requer ADMIN)
# Sintaxe 'e-mail:senha' corrige o erro 401
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/accounts/directory
Authorization: Basic {{rootEmail}}:{{rootPass}}

### 3. Buscar Perfil Específico
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/accounts/profile/{{subscriberUid}}
Authorization: Basic {{clientEmail}}:{{clientPass}}

### ============================================================================
### 📈 GESTÃO DE ATIVOS FINANCEIROS (HOLDINGS)
### ============================================================================

### 1. Registrar Aquisição de Ativo
# Alinhado com o HoldingInputDTO e AssetManagementService
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/assets/execute
Authorization: Basic {{clientEmail}}:{{clientPass}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "assetCategory": "STOCK",
  "ticker": "VALE3",
  "volume": 50,
  "acquisitionCost": 65.50,
  "entryDate": "2026-02-22"
}

### 2. Listar Histórico de Ativos
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/assets/list-all
Authorization: Basic {{rootEmail}}:{{rootPass}}

### 3. Obter Resumo da Saúde da Carteira (Health Check)
# Anteriormente bloqueado por Erro 401
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/assets/health
Authorization: Basic {{clientEmail}}:{{clientPass}}

### ============================================================================
### 💼 CARTEIRAS DE INVESTIMENTO (WALLETS)
### ============================================================================

### 1. Inicializar/Vincular Carteira ao Usuário
# Vincula a WalletEntity ao SubscriberEntity via ownerId
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/wallets/open
Authorization: Basic {{clientEmail}}:{{clientPass}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "ownerId": "{{subscriberUid}}",
  "aggregatedValue": 3275.00,
  "distributionMap": {
    "STOCK": 3275.00
  },
  "totalQuantity": 50,
  "holdings": [
    {
      "assetCategory": "STOCK",
      "ticker": "VALE3",
      "volume": 50,
      "acquisitionCost": 65.50,
      "entryDate": "2026-02-22"
    }
  ]
}

### 2. Sincronizar Dados da Carteira
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/wallets/sync/{{walletUid}}
Authorization: Basic {{clientEmail}}:{{clientPass}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "ownerId": "{{subscriberUid}}",
  "aggregatedValue": 6550.00,
  "distributionMap": {
    "STOCK": 6550.00
  },
  "totalQuantity": 100,
  "holdings": [
    {
      "assetCategory": "STOCK",
      "ticker": "VALE3",
      "volume": 100,
      "acquisitionCost": 65.50,
      "entryDate": "2026-02-22"
    }
  ]
}